N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5102.18 - Application to change video lottery gaming license

State Regulations
A video lottery gaming licensee may apply to change the
status of such licensee's current license by filing an application in a form
prescribed by the commission. Notes
